nodes.text: A Consular-class cruiser was used by Jedi Master Mavra Zane to transport a group of younglings to the Jedi outpost on Kashyyyk around 22 BBY. She tested them during the trip by using training remotes. The cruiser also carried Delta-7 Aethersprite-class light interceptors aboard.
The Consular-class cruiser appears in the Jedi Destiny portion of Kinect Star Wars.
